WorkItem.Summary: GMap with GoogleSatelliteMap provider not working?

Comments.Message:
Thank radioman for your reply...
why not gmap issue?! clearly it's not working as it should be

check http://greatmaps.codeplex.com/discussions/636171#post1423562

if you want to help to solve the issue, you can try run fiddler, then use web browser and go to the same test area and post http request log on forum

then you need to run gmap.net and post output log, so we can compare requests

in theory request should be the same

thanks

Chances are if it works one place and not another it's something in that environment.
I had a similar issue with my system. After ruling out network issues I found this command you can run from the terminal (Administrative terminal) __netsh winsock reset__ . After rebooting my issue was cleared up.
